# Experimental!
S ← 300
# Create SxS grid, and set central seed.
∧⍜⊡⋅1+⌟♭₂˙⊞⊟-2⇡5↯2⌊÷2S ↯ S_S 0
EdgePoint ← (⍥⇌⁅⚂⊂⨬(0|-1S)⁅⚂⌊×⚂ S) # Use () to indicate fn, not const.
MakeLine  ← ⊚◡⊡⊙(◌◌)⌊⊸+⌟×⌟⇡⟜÷/↥⊸⌵◡-EdgePoint EdgePoint
HitTree   ← ⍜⊡⋅1⊡-1⊢⍢(MakeLine◌◌|=0⧻)MakeLine

⍜now(▽₂2⍥HitTree20000)
